public class TumblerRunner
extends org.junit.runners.BlockJUnit4ClassRunner

JUnit runner. Represents stories and scenarios as sentences in JUnit GUIs. May also generate scenarios' statuses report in .scenarios or html format if -DgenerateReport=[scenario|html] is passed while running scenarios. The output folder for the report can be configured by setting -DoutputFolder property. If -DcamelCase is passed, IDEs will show class and method names instead of scenario and story names.

Author:
Pawel Lipinski
